{
  "stem": "19518.5",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Nobody shows up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "We only see jeeps passing by to the forest, motorcycles going by to the forest on the other road, not the road near us.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "But we don't see anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We don't know anybody.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We don't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "We're standing there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "We're standing there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "Now, when night came, the woman, the blockova was afraid that some of us will take a walk-- where to, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] But she was afraid of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "So she made us go back into the barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "Because at least this way she knew where we were.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "They never came to count us again.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "Because next morning we heard-- and through the night we heard gun-- guns.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "We knew that-- we had the feeling that the war is coming to an end.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But we did not know how and when.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And we also knew that as long as the Germans are near us, we are not certain that we will survive.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "We are not certain that we will live, that we will be allowed to live.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "That somewheres along the line, they'll always find a way to grab hold of us and finish us off.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] But there was no escape for us whatsoever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Now, Saturday morning, again, they lined us up to be counted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "Nobody showed up.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And we were-- and it was a nice spring day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "We were standing outside.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And the blockova wasn't there anymore.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Somewheres along the night I guess her lover came for her, and they left.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And around noon time, a-- a motorcycle for two stopped by our gate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "SS men went out to the one who was on-- on guard, pulled off his insignias, and the other one pulled his insignias off.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "They got onto the motorcycle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "They disappeared.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
